Package network

Class Connection

  • java.lang.Object
    • network.Connection
  • public class Connection
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains the vital information to be stored for each active connection. Each Player in a game has a nickName, identifier, and a boolean isMyTurn which are necessary to maintain turn order, especially if a player reconnects should an issue be encountered. The lists of lists are used in notify methods within socket connections.
